title: Virat Kohli And Anushka Sharma Delhi Reception Today At This Hotel
tags: the durbar hall|"taj diplomatic enclave"|"virat-anuhska reception"|"virushka reception"|"delhi reception today"|"pm modi"|"guest list"|"reception card"|"narendra modi"|"virat kohli"|"anushka sharma"|"india national cricket team"|"2 minute news today"|"2mnewstoday"|"entertainment news"|"cricket"
description:
Virat Kohli And Anushka Sharma Delhi Reception Today At This Hotel
समाचार:  The Durbar Hall of Taj Diplomatic Enclave will host Virat-Anuhska Reception Today in Delhi
दिल्ली के इस होटल में आज विराट-अनुष्का का रिसेप्शन, गेस्ट में PM मोदी भी
विराट कोहली और अनुष्का शर्मा का पहला वेडिंग रिसेप्शन आज शाम दिल्ली में होगा। दूसरा रिसेप्शन 26 दिसंबर को मुंबई में है।
Team India captain Virat Kohli's first wedding reception will be held this evening in Delhi. These receptions will be in the Darbar Hall of the Taj Diplomatic Enclave here. Beautiful artwork is done inside this hotel in the Mughal period. The hotel has 292 luxury rooms. More than 1000 guests can visit this hall. According to the card, the reception 8 dot starts at 30 o'clock.
Virat Kohli has also invited Prime Minister Narendra Modi in this reception. On returning to India on December 19, Virat Wife had visited the PM along with Anushka on Wednesday. Both gave them an invitation to their reception. During this time Virat was accompanied by his elder brother Vikas Kohli.
Explain that Kapal has only invited special guests, relatives and close friends in Delhi reception. The second reception will be held in Mumbai on December 26. Here is the hope of reaching all the celebrities of cricket and Bollywood world.
This may be the menu
The Taj Hotel has different food arrangements in different halls. Where Virat-Anushka reception party will be, the food is completely North Indian.
Punjabi cuisine will be special in the evening serving dishes. It is worth mentioning that Virat is Punjabi and there is a great fondness for eating.
Kapal married in Italy on December 11. After this Virat-Anushka went for honeymoon. Now after the Mumbai reception, Anushka Sharma will also accompany Virat to South Africa. Team India has to play Tests, ODIs and T20 series here. Virat will remain in South Africa for nearly two months, while Anushka will return after the New Year.

Indian pace spear Mohammad Shami has been in the limelight for the last few days because of his wife's allegations. Shami's wife Hussein, who has accused her of extramarital affair as well as domestic violence.
Haseen has also shared some pictures and messages from Shami on social media. It has been said that Shami's affair is with a Pakistani woman.
At the same time, Shami is telling these allegations baseless. Shami says that this conspiracy is being hatched to spoil his image.
On seeing Haseen, Shami gave him his heart and both of them got married in 2014. Haseen was born in a Bengali Muslim family of Kolkata. In Kolkata itself, Hasin started her modeling career. You will be surprised to know that Mohammed Shami Hassin is the second husband of Hasin's first marriage did not last long and she was divorced from her husband. His first husband had objection to his modeling.
Haasin's dream was to work in films, but during the ongoing IPL in 2012, he met Shami and both of them fell in love with each other. Hasin used to work as cheerleader for the KKR team in those days.
After two years of affair, both of them got married on June 6, 2014 with the consent of their families. On behalf of Mohammad Shami's father Tausif Ahmad, Haseen left the modeling career too.
Hussein also chose to leave modeling and live as a house wife after marriage. Tell me that Hasin has made several serious allegations against Shami. He also disclosed about Shami's relationship with many women, while also threatening to kill himself and kill him. However, Shami says that this is just being done to ruin his career

description:
Everyone deserves a great love story. But for seventeen-year old Simon Spier it’s a little more complicated: he’s yet to tell his family or friends he’s gay and he doesn’t actually know the identity of the anonymous classmate he’s fallen for online. Resolving both issues proves hilarious, terrifying and life-changing. Directed by Greg Berlanti (Dawson’s Creek, Brothers & Sisters), written by Isaac Aptaker & Elizabeth Berger (This is Us), and based on Becky Albertalli’s acclaimed novel, LOVE, SIMON is a funny and heartfelt coming-of-age story about the thrilling ride of finding yourself and falling in love.

In Theaters March 16, 2018

Cast: Nick Robinson, Katherine Langford, Alexandra Shipp, Jorge Lendeborg, Miles Heizer, Keiynan Lonsdale, Logan Miller, Jennifer Garner, Josh Duhamel, Tony Hale.

Directed by: Greg Berlanti

Screenplay by: Isaac Aptaker and Elizabeth Berger

Produced by: Wyck Godfrey and Marty Bowen

Searching to regain his spice for life, as well as a flux capacitor, Wade must battle ninjas, the yakuza, and a pack of sexually aggressive canines, as he journeys around the world to discover the importance of family, friendship, and flavor – finding a new taste for adventure and earning the coveted coffee mug title of World’s Best Lover. 

In Theaters May 18, 2018

description:
Jabardast program comedian, Rocking Rajesh said that there were no financial problems for comedian Vijay Sai, who had committed suicide last night. He said that he was a sensitive person and only family disputes, with his wife, might have led him to the extreme step. Vijay Sai has acted in a number of films, including Bommarillu. His tiff with his wife has gone up to divorce and there was wrangling over alimony, it is said. All this and lack of offers might have caused depression, ending in suicide, it is believed.

description:
Hyderabad: Tollywood comedian Vijay Sai committed suicide by hanging self from ceiling at his residence in Yousufguda area of Hyderabad. The 38-year-old took to the extreme step on early Monday morning.

His parents blamed his estranged wife Vanitha Reddy for his suicide. Two days ago, Sai had lodged a complaint with the Jubilee Hills police that Vanitha had forcibly taken away his car from the parking lot without his knowledge. Vijay is learnt to have shot a video before ending his life. He has named three persons responsible for his extreme step. Vanitha, her lawyer and a private person were named in the video.
